OL,3,CPresbyterian Church to hold Belfast
OL,4,Cassembly to update on safeguarding
OL,5,Cfailings
OL,7,FThe Presbyterian Church in Ireland is
OL,8,Fto hold its second congregation-wide
OL,9,Fmeeting in Belfast to hear an update
OL,10,Fon failings in safeguarding processes.
OL,12,FThe Special General Assembly on
OL,13,FWednesday will address a range of
OL,14,Fissues, with ministers and a
OL,15,Frepresentative elder from each of the
OL,16,Fall-Ireland denomination's 500-plus
OL,17,Fcongregations entitled to attend the
OL,18,Fmeeting.
