OL,7,FMembers will receive an update on
OL,8,Fsafeguarding and progress regarding
OL,9,Fthe General Council task groups that
OL,10,Fwere set up as a result of decisions
OL,11,Ftaken at December's Special Assembly.
OL,13,FAt that assembly, David Bruce, a
OL,14,Fretired minister and Convener of the
OL,15,FGeneral Council, said questions around
OL,16,Fsafeguarding at the church "became
OL,17,Fmuch more acute" in 2025 when a person
OL,18,Fwas convicted of child sexual abuse
OL,19,Foffences and was imprisoned.
