OL,7,FSpeaking ahead of the meeting on
OL,8,FWednesday, Dr Bruce said, "As we move
OL,9,Fforward from November's announcement
OL,10,Fof our central safeguarding failures,
OL,11,Fand decisions taken at our December
OL,12,FSpecial General Assembly, it is
OL,13,Fimportant that we update the Church on
OL,14,Fwhat has been done in the intervening
OL,15,Fweeks, and this will be part of my
OL,16,Freport."
OL,18,FHe added: "Alongside the update on
OL,19,Fprogress, there are two principal
OL,20,Fitems of business before today's
OL,21,Fmeeting.
