OL,7,F"When the Moderator, Dr Murray, called
OL,8,Fthis Special Assembly he said that it
OL,9,Fwould consider the ceremonial and
OL,10,Freporting aspects of our General
OL,11,FAssembly in June and the 'urgent
OL,12,Fmatter of approving the appointment
OL,13,Fprocess of a new Clerk of the General
OL,14,FAssembly', and these will be discussed.
