OL,4,Cassembly to update on safeguarding
OL,5,Cfailings
OL,7,F"While there won't be, at this stage,
OL,8,Fitems of business regarding
OL,9,Fsafeguarding, or other reports from
OL,10,Fthe various task groups established by
OL,11,FDecember's Special Assembly, the
OL,12,Fbusiness before us today is more than
OL,13,Fsimple 'housekeeping'."
OL,15,F"The role of Clerk of the General
OL,16,FAssembly, for example, is an historic
OL,17,Fposition within our denomination, to
OL,18,Fwhich we are proposing, significant
OL,19,Fchanges," Dr Bruce said.
