OL,7,FThe former Moderator concluded by
OL,8,Fsaying: "In all that we do, we remain
OL,9,Fdeeply mindful of those who have been
OL,10,Fhurt or harmed as a result of our
OL,11,Ffailings.
OL,13,F"As I said at December's Special
OL,14,FAssembly, our starting point was and
OL,15,Fremains a profound concern for those
OL,16,Fwho have been harmed, or impacted by
OL,17,Four institutional failings, which I
OL,18,Fdescribed as shameful.
